gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97abc3bc4b7b967d77692e0ec7cb3c75929d550","tid":1724194,"uid":86828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjWxQgi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjWxQgi.jpg&h=9475caf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抗爭大台/領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee1a0c8b2e9dde623c2c60b7fbcbcfece5b0e76","tid":1724194,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"設獨立調查委員會 還看北京 (轉載節錄)<br />\n過去這個夏天，不少香港人流汗、流淚甚至流血，成千上萬群眾在街頭吶喊過無數次，高呼「五大訴求 缺一不可」，要求政府回應。五大訴求中，由於當局已經撤回《逃犯條例》修訂，若說設獨立調查委員會（COI）是港人訴求的最大公因數，相信無人會反對。儘管連月來民意非常清晰，但港府高層繼續置若罔聞或稱「不是此時」.....<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟發夢幻想有一個城市個失去警察公信力既情況:<br />\n<br />\n如果市民認為警察公信力盡失，由警方做任何「獨立」監管或調查都未必能令社會平息暴力。但政府遲遲不做只係因為怕警隊出現反抗...而反抗後果係:<br />\n<br />\n1. 警察大罷工，然後市面上會「突然」出現非常多的罪案，犯罪者是誰 ? 大家可以思考下，而令社會「回復」和平的代價就係取消獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察持槍大遊行，你懂的<br />\n<br />\n可否用軍方力量整冶? 我認為認為係可以<br />\n客觀分析，其實未必冇可能，國家領導層能一石二鳥，一可以化解民怨，二可建立一個訊息比大家知，就係只係一直都只係警察前線胡作非為冇聽上頭指示，不失為得民心之方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於軍方力量點清算，可以有2個方法:<br />\n1. 混入前線 (包括滲透內部相同意見人仕)，係執行職務時搜集證據，交由獨立委員會清算<br />\n2. 係前線下班後用武力拘捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭你諗諗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習主席都可能好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2de2e7a779565ebd9fb9d0c908abde9bfddba46","tid":1724194,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a45d37c84fb4b158dfabd16f5f9424809a68116e","tid":1724194,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HN5O3oF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHN5O3oF.png&h=f4c78353&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a34d3776cd56f944aa8a49a349757d062a8832b","tid":1724194,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"仲有普京<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}